Since you're still having issues, it's more likely that there's a local network setting that's preventing your client from reaching the login server correctly. In this case, you should ensure your network is up to spec with our [connection guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if anything changed.
